Having trouble paying your tax debt in full? Try our new, easy to use, Payment Arrangement Calculator to help you figure out different payment scenarios depending on:
• How much you can afford to pay;
• The frequency you wish to make your payments, (weekly, bi-weekly, or monthly), and;
• How to pay off your debt in the fastest way possible (within 6 to 24 months) to limit the amount of interest you pay. 
